summary:
For the past 9 years, I’ve worked with 100+ startups, along with the majority of top VCs/corporations in CEE. I started my journey with my own projects, but soon discovered that my real passion is helping others. 
​
I cooperated with startups on both sides - as a corporate and startup representative. My corporate career started in Carrefour (French retail chain), where I coordinated relationships with startups, co-created the first Poland Retail focused incubator, and led more than 20 startup projects. I then joined Microsoft, and as the Head of Startups in Poland, I managed and helped to grow 60+ startups in the program. 
​
I was responsible for shaping a 2-year program to ensure startups grew and flourished in that time. I engaged with various partners in the startup ecosystem, developing offerings to support engagement and attract high-potential startups, including mentorship, and Go-to-Market support.
​
Now I decided to support projects that I believe in. 
How can I help you?
